    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dings, and that new-car smell is still lingering. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
