      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless showroom shine. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips or swirls, while the interior remains in pristine condition, still carrying that fresh, new-car scent. Every stitch in the premium leather is taut and perfect, and the electronic interfaces remain scratch-free. Mechanically, the car performs with whisper-quiet precision, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a meticulous driver to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. No stories, no excuses\u2014just a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
