    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Check out this absolute beauty! I'm parting ways with my pride and joy, and honestly, she's in pristine condition. It's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014no scratches, no weird noises, just pure perfection. I've babied this car since day one with regular detailing and careful driving, and I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. It's ready to hit the road with zero worries, so come take a look!",
