    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S54 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is superlative; the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings and Vanos system have been overhauled to exceed factory specifications. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with notch-free precision, paired with a fresh clutch and a perfectly dialed-in limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry without any bushing deflection or fluid seepage. Every heat shield, fastener, and gasket reflects a vehicle that has been maintained in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the high-revving 8,000 RPM redline is met with seamless power delivery and zero parasitic loss. This is a collector-grade example for those who prioritize mechanical purity and tactile feedback.",
